defaultThe Republic of Ireland has the highest rate of tobacco duty in the EU, followed by the UK
default.
defaultThe UK has some of the hig
defaulthest tobacco taxes in the world, with 
defaulttax accounting for up to 
default88% of the RRP
default on some brands
default. 
defaultThe fall
defaulting rate of the illicit market
default has continued despite rising tobacco taxes and consequent high prices in the same period.
